The Vice President, Mike Pence, delivered a speech at the Heritage Foundation Honors Gala, where he thanked the organization for their support and highlighted the accomplishments of the Trump administration. He praised the administration's efforts in national defense, economic growth, border security, and the appointment of conservative judges. Pence also emphasized the importance of freedom and the dangers of socialism. He urged the audience to continue advocating for conservative principles and to support President Trump for another term in office.